Industries We Serve

Captive insurance structures can be tailored to virtually any industry. We work with organizations across sectors to create customized risk management solutions that address industry-specific challenges.

Manufacturing

Production and equipment-related risks, worker safety, and operational continuity.

Transportation & Logistics

Construction

Project-specific risks, equipment liability, and contractor oversight.

Healthcare

Professional liability, property coverage, and specialized medical industry risks.

Real Estate & Property Management

Multi-property coverage, liability protection, and loss prevention.

Professional Services

Errors and omissions, client liability, and specialized service coverage.
